<div class="govuk-width-container">
  <%= partial "shared/get-help/breadcrumbs", locals: { page: "Connect with an Android device" } %>
  <div class="govuk-main-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
      <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
          <%= partial 'shared/get-help/sidebar' %>
      </div>
      <main class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds" role="main" id="main">
        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Connect to GovWifi with an Android device</h1>
        <p class="govuk-body">
          Your device should connect automatically when you select <strong>GovWifi</strong> from your list of available wifi networks and enter your GovWifi password.
        </p>
        <p class="govuk-body">
          If your device doesn't connect automatically:
        </p>
        <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">If your device doesn't connect automaticaly, open your wifi settings.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Select <strong>GovWifi</strong>. A settings menu should appear.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>EAP method</strong>, select <strong>PEAP</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>Phase 2 authentication</strong>, select <strong>MSCHAPV2</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>CA Certificate</strong>, ensure <strong>(unspecified)</strong> or <strong>Do not validate</strong> is selected.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">If your device asks for your <strong>Domain</strong>, enter <strong>wifi.service.gov.uk</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>Identity</strong>, enter the GovWifi username you received by email or text.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Leave <strong>Anonymous identity</strong> blank.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Scroll down. Enter the username and password you received by email or text.</p>
            <p class="govuk-inset-text">Your password is case sensitive. It's 3 words without spaces. The first letter of each word is capitalised.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Select <strong>Connect</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="govuk-body">
            You should now be connected to Govwifi.
          </p>
          <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Support</h2>
          <p class="govuk-body">
            If you still have problems connecting to GovWifi, contact the IT support desk for the building you're in.
          </p>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
